item.title: My First Article!
item.description: This post marks the beginning of my blog! I will post things I learn from my hobbies and any interesting tidbits as I progress through the field of Computer Science!! You can find my links at https://links.jenspot.com

item.title: About me
item.description: I am a 2nd year computer science student at the University of Leeds. I am currently working on: Adding more content to my blog Adding features to my implementation of Conway’s Game of Life Creating my site index page for https://jenspot.com Building and deploying an environmental sensor system based on an arduino Tidying my code for my custom macro keyboard
